<item>
            <title>[LU-16108] Require change on default dom_stripesize</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16108</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Need assistance in changing default dom_stripesize for lustre MDT.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;No option found on our servers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;[root@lustre_dev ~]# lctl get_param lod.*MDT0000*.dom_stripesize
error: get_param: param_path &apos;lod/*MDT0000*/dom_stripesize&apos;: No such file or directory
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Searched for lod parameter &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl get_param -R &apos;&amp;#42;&apos;|grep -i lod&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; but it does not exist.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Can you please assist as i need to change the mdt value above the default 1MB ?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Thanks&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>DEV</environment>
